(see Jerome, *Præf. in Paralipom., Apol. adv. Ruf.* II. 27, *Præf in
quattuor Evangelia;* and cf. *Comment. in Isaiam,* LVIII. 11). We know
little about this text; but Jerome speaks of it slightingly, as does
